        "setup": "Get it from the Fly dashboard: go to [Tokens](https://fly.io/dashboard), choose your organization, then create an organization token and copy it. For CLI access, `fly auth login` can also mint the login session that `flyctl` uses; the Machines API docs show `fly tokens deploy` for a deploy-scoped token. Use the token as `Authorization: Bearer ...` or via `FLY_API_TOKEN` / `FLY_ACCESS_TOKEN` depending on the surface.",
